address.streetAddress: Millhaven Plan, The Grove at Neill's Pointe

location.fullValue: Millhaven Plan, The Grove at Neill's Pointe

data.description: 4 bed 2.5 bath traditional style home in convenient Angier location. Hardwood style floors throughout most of 1st floor. Large family room features gas log fireplace. Formal dining room. Bright & open eat-in kitchen offers granite countertops, freshly painted cabinets & stainless steel appliances. Spacious primary suite with vaulted ceiling, dual vanities, tiled soaking tub/shower and walk in closet. 3 additional ample sized bedrooms. 9 foot ceilings. Recently installed SOLAR PANELS give this home extremely low energy bills. Rainsoft water softener. New heat pump 2021. Nest thermostats. Private, fenced backyard has patio and storage shed with great wooded views. Steps from upcoming new Angier Town Park including multiple baseball fields, pickleball/tennis courts, dog park, playgrounds, dog park, nature playground & trails.
